title: DAZ3D - Raoul for Ivan 7 HD
description:
Raoul for Ivan 7 HD
-------------------
 
https://cdn.pximg.xyz/ef534b0a1f604becaa56b84f9e284d80.jpg

www.daz3d.com/catalog/product/view/id/32409

Raoul is a high-quality character for the unique and incredible Ivan 7 HD. If you need a bruiser, bodyguard, fighter, raider or just an intimidating presence and someone to throw their weight around, Raoul has all situations covered and he gets the job done. Raoul comes with highly-detailed textures with several face and body options, including clean, battered, and bloody options. The blood options use the LIE (Layered Image Editor) so there may be a momentary delay when selecting these options. Raoul uses the HD morphs for Ivan 7 in all of his promos. He still looks excellent without the HD morphs, but lacks the grizzled, aging features
